                            GFX-Lab 24 v1.8.1

                         Rodrigo REYES 1994-1995


       GFXLab24 is an image  processing  program,  written  for AMIGA
       computers  with  system  3.0  or  more.  This program is freely
       distributable as long as no changes are made on the software
       or on its documentation. ANY distribution in a magazine cover
       disk must be submitted to the agreement of the author.
       Distribution in a commercial package is not authorized, and
       will not be.



